806
00:58:00,810 --> 00:58:03,312
Get up, l say

807
00:58:04,731 --> 00:58:06,315
Get up

808
00:58:06,399 --> 00:58:07,232
What's happening?

809
00:58:07,317 --> 00:58:08,525
This man is a nuisance

810
00:58:08,568 --> 00:58:10,402
He brought the bench
from the veranda to sleep here

811
00:58:10,487 --> 00:58:12,654
Lock me up
Or, l will sleep here

812
00:58:12,697 --> 00:58:15,032
l always sleep at ten
after a glass of milk

813
00:58:15,658 --> 00:58:16,575
Go

814
00:58:18,453 --> 00:58:21,288
This is sheer menace and
l already wrote out the FlR!

815
00:58:22,457 --> 00:58:24,333
lf you want to get out
get someone to bail you

816
00:58:24,417 --> 00:58:26,585
