821
00:58:40,975 --> 00:58:43,060
Who is it, middle ofthe night?!

822
00:58:44,270 --> 00:58:47,523
lf it is anyone important
ask him to call tomorrow, l'm offto sleep

823
00:58:48,525 --> 00:58:49,816
Hello, who is it?

824
00:58:51,486 --> 00:58:55,155
lsn't this the number of Venu
stinger cameraman, of Reuters?

825
00:59:00,161 --> 00:59:02,663
Who is it, sir?
ls it from the orphanage?

826
00:59:03,915 --> 00:59:04,623
Hello?

827
00:59:08,127 --> 00:59:10,712
l am advocate, Manilal
