828
00:59:10,797 --> 00:59:15,759
Counsel, it was a mistake
Please ask him to overlook this

829
00:59:15,969 --> 00:59:19,846
My police pal, see what happens
when you confront me, at midnight?

830
00:59:19,889 --> 00:59:21,348
- Did you see now?
- Heard now?

831
00:59:22,225 --> 00:59:23,100
Thanks a lot

832
00:59:24,852 --> 00:59:25,435
venu?

833
00:59:27,564 --> 00:59:30,774
l've been trying you from
last evening but couldn't get through

834
00:59:30,858 --> 00:59:32,067
Who are you?

835
00:59:32,151 --> 00:59:34,695
l am advocate, Manilal
l have something to tell you

836
00:59:34,737 --> 00:59:35,821
What is it?

837
00:59:36,322 --> 00:59:37,489
lt's about an exclusive

838
00:59:37,699 --> 00:59:40,367
However important it is
l'll see you tomorrow...

839
00:59:40,451 --> 00:59:43,036
...when l am fresh
Come let's go!

840
00:59:58,052 --> 01:00:00,178
So tell me, what is this
exclusive, all about?

841
01:00:00,305 --> 01:00:04,099
An exclusive like this won't ever occur
in the history of news channels again

842
01:00:04,601 --> 01:00:06,560
A story that has
to be shot risking life

843
01:00:06,936 --> 01:00:11,148
l've risked my life many times
Forget that, come to the point

844
01:00:11,232 --> 01:00:15,611
l will, but before that, l want
a firm affirmation from you

845
01:00:17,405 --> 01:00:20,824
This exclusive info was got
from a particular channel

846
01:00:21,326 --> 01:00:23,243
The story has to be
covered, only forthem

847
01:00:23,870 --> 01:00:27,289
Their reporterwill accompany you
Do you have any objections?

848
01:00:29,167 --> 01:00:32,210
Once l disclose information
You can't go back on your word

849
01:00:32,420 --> 01:00:37,424
Mr lawyer, l do follow certain ethics
lf l give my word, it is forever

850
01:00:37,592 --> 01:00:38,550
So you agree?

851
01:00:39,302 --> 01:00:40,093
Agreed

852
01:00:41,095 --> 01:00:44,222
But l'll be the one to decide
what to do and how to do it

853
01:00:44,265 --> 01:00:45,641
Okay, agreed

854
01:00:59,614 --> 01:01:04,868
