ofa well known politician of Kerala

856
01:01:13,336 --> 01:01:16,588
Sorry! l cannot do this

857
01:01:16,673 --> 01:01:18,507
Hey! venu!
Please!

858
01:01:18,549 --> 01:01:20,509
A life is more important
than a piece of news

859
01:01:20,551 --> 01:01:23,553
Since we have info,
we have to try and save him

860
01:01:23,805 --> 01:01:27,391
lt may lessen the news value, but
ratings mustn't depend on blood spilt

861
01:01:27,433 --> 01:01:29,101
venu, let me explain

862
01:01:37,443 --> 01:01:41,446
lt's not my urge to make money
by 'live' coverage ofa man's death

863
01:01:41,781 --> 01:01:46,368
He can't be saved by anyone
even if it's reported to the police

864
01:01:46,619 --> 01:01:52,082
Because, Bharathan Pillai still dictates,
even though, he's not yet Chief Minister

865
01:01:53,876 --> 01:01:55,335
- Bharathan Pillai?
-Yes

866
01:01:55,628 --> 01:01:57,587
This murderwill
take place on his behalf

867
01:01:57,630 --> 01:02:02,509
We can't prevent it, can't we at least
make sure the culprits don't escape?

868
01:02:07,098 --> 01:02:08,473
Okay, so who is the victim?

869
01:02:08,933 --> 01:02:12,227
A man in Bharathan Pillai's group
We don't know who orwhat...

870
01:02:12,311 --> 01:02:13,478
What rubbish is this?

871
01:02:14,021 --> 01:02:17,858
l can only assure you
this information is 100% genuine

872
01:02:20,778 --> 01:02:25,699
Tell me the place, time and date and
who is the reporter, coming with me

873
01:02:26,701 --> 01:02:27,409
Renu?

874
01:02:36,794 --> 01:02:37,586
This woman?!

875
01:02:38,671 --> 01:02:42,048
Find someone else!
Lawyer, drop me back!

876
01:02:42,133 --> 01:02:47,929
venu, listen to me
You can't go, you agreed...

877
01:02:48,014 --> 01:02:51,725
...l disclosed info because
you claimed to have ethics

878
01:02:51,768 --> 01:02:53,852
Did you tell me before hand
this useless creature was coming?

879
01:02:53,936 --> 01:02:55,395
You only said some reporter

880
01:02:55,980 --> 01:03:00,776
Didn't l warn you to disclose info
only after telling him everything, Chey!

881
01:03:01,360 --> 01:03:07,365
Think it's not Renuka, but a stranger
X orY, with a professional approach

882
01:03:07,492 --> 01:03:13,038
l am totally professional! Such a riskyjob,
l need someone who gels with me

883
01:03:13,623 --> 01:03:15,916
Petty personal issues
mustn't come in the way...

884
01:03:15,958 --> 01:03:19,795
...ofthis exclusive with
such strong social impact

885
01:03:19,962 --> 01:03:22,464
We don't have any option, but Renuka

886
01:03:25,802 --> 01:03:28,261
venu, you can insist on
whatever conditions you want

887
01:03:29,764 --> 01:03:30,722
Please

888
01:03:34,685 --> 01:03:35,644
Please venu!

889
01:03:39,065 --> 01:03:39,606
Okay

890
01:03:41,067 --> 01:03:45,821
These are my conditions
l'll be the sole decision maker

891
01:03:46,155 --> 01:03:49,366
Reporter X or Y is not allowed
to make any suggestions

892
01:03:50,409 --> 01:03:51,201
Sure

893
01:03:51,786 --> 01:03:55,497
A DSNG van, without any crew
must be at my disposal

894
01:03:56,791 --> 01:03:57,541
Okay

895
01:03:58,334 --> 01:04:03,713
visuals l 'UP' has to be aired, unedited
With no interference in it, whatsoever

896
01:04:04,549 --> 01:04:05,632
Agreed

897
01:04:05,967 --> 01:04:08,927
My remuneration alone, is Rs 10 lakh

898
01:04:10,513 --> 01:04:14,766
- Here, it's got more than what you've asked
- Let it wait, there are more conditions

899
01:04:15,560 --> 01:04:18,019
visuals must accompany
a scrolling script...

900
01:04:18,271 --> 01:04:21,648
'visuals exclusively covered
by cameraman venu'

901
01:04:22,525 --> 01:04:25,819
No intro or sign out by the reporter

902
01:04:26,487 --> 01:04:27,237
Agreed

903
01:04:32,034 --> 01:04:36,121
You have 12 hours to plan
and prepare, Renu knows the details

904
01:04:36,205 --> 01:04:36,830
Okay

905
01:04:36,998 --> 01:04:38,790
The baton has now
shifted into your hands

906
01:04:38,958 --> 01:04:41,042
venu...Renu?
Shake hands on this

907
01:04:41,168 --> 01:04:42,085
Not necessary!

908
01:04:42,169 --> 01:04:44,588
What's this? You'll be
working together hereafter

909
01:04:44,672 --> 01:04:45,547
Be professional

910
01:04:45,631 --> 01:04:47,048
venu please?

911
01:05:01,147 --> 01:05:02,647
Keep the cash in the car

912
01:05:03,399 --> 01:05:07,235
You have neither an intro nor sign off
Why the hell are you tagging along?

913
01:05:08,154 --> 01:05:12,282
Suppose you run away with the footage
as a revenge forthe old grouse?

914
01:05:12,783 --> 01:05:16,661
There is only 1 creature on earth
who'd do such things, and that's you!

915
01:05:17,246 --> 01:05:21,458
l forgot to tell you, DSNG receives
poor signal at the crime spot

916
01:05:21,542 --> 01:05:25,003
