01:05:26,088 --> 01:05:28,965
Okay, now both of you
can chart out a plan

919
01:05:29,133 --> 01:05:31,426
Not 'both' of us
Only me!

920
01:05:52,615 --> 01:05:54,282
- Shall l suggest something?
- No!

921
01:05:54,784 --> 01:05:56,201
- Listen first
- Not necessary

922
01:05:57,620 --> 01:05:59,704
