and just allow me to do my stuff

932
01:06:26,941 --> 01:06:27,857
To hell with you!

933
01:06:53,551 --> 01:06:59,347
Lean back and sit without
touching me, especially your bust!

934
01:07:00,057 --> 01:07:02,267
You dirty...chi!!!

935
01:07:21,579 --> 01:07:22,746
Turn left

936
01:07:24,623 --> 01:07:26,583
This is the club house

937
01:07:27,168 --> 01:07:28,793
