966
01:13:18,477 --> 01:13:22,730
Will your confessions
give me back, all what l lost?

967
01:13:22,815 --> 01:13:28,111
My image, position, the days l spent
idle at home, since last 5 years

968
01:13:29,196 --> 01:13:32,407
Suguna, to you, wasn't it
just an itch on your tongue?

969
01:13:35,619 --> 01:13:39,122
